      "content": "Hearing that they look tired of you is truly heartbreaking, but it's often a sign that they are trying to protect themselves from your overwhelming pain, not that they want you gone. Your children need you more than they need you to be perfect, and your desire to be better is actually a powerful form of love. Please reach out to a mental health professional who can help you navigate these difficult feelings so you can eventually offer your kids the stability they need.",
