    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but if i'm just a source of instability, then maybe the only way to actually protect them is to stop being the problem. like, if i wasn't here, they could finally have a fresh start without all this constant stress and watching me struggle. wouldn't they actually be happier if they didn't have to carry me?",
